### Common Violations and Fixes

**Underscore Usage (Wrong Separator):**
` ``text
❌ readme_file.md              →  ✅ readme-file.md
❌ contributing_guide.md       →  ✅ contributing-guide.md
❌ api_documentation.md        →  ✅ api-documentation.md
❌ security_policy.md          →  ✅ security-policy.md
` ``

**Capitalization Violations:**
` ``text
❌ README.md                   →  ✅ readme.md
❌ CONTRIBUTING.md             →  ✅ contributing.md
❌ LICENSE.md                  →  ✅ license.md
❌ API-Reference.md            →  ✅ api-reference.md
` ``

**CamelCase Violations:**
` ``text
❌ apiDocumentation.md         →  ✅ api-documentation.md
❌ securityPolicy.md           →  ✅ security-policy.md
❌ codeOfConduct.md            →  ✅ code-of-conduct.md
❌ contributingGuide.md        →  ✅ contributing-guide.md
` ``

**Space and Special Character Violations:**
` ``text
❌ API Documentation.md        →  ✅ api-documentation.md
❌ Security Policy.md          →  ✅ security-policy.md
❌ Code of Conduct.md          →  ✅ code-of-conduct.md
❌ file.backup.md              →  ✅ file-backup.md
` ``

### Validation Commands

**Find Non-Compliant Markdown Files:**
` ``bash
# Find markdown files with underscores
find . -type f -name "*.md" | grep "_"

# Find markdown files with uppercase
find . -type f -name "*.md" | grep -E "[A-Z]"

# Find markdown files with spaces
find . -type f -name "* *.md"

# Find markdown files with multiple dots
find . -type f -name "*.*.md"
` ``

**Batch Rename Non-Compliant Files:**
` ``bash
# Convert underscores to dashes
for file in $(find . -type f -name "*_*.md"); do
  newname=$(echo "$file" | sed 's/_/-/g')
  mv "$file" "$newname"
done

# Convert to lowercase
for file in $(find . -type f -name "*.md" | grep -E "[A-Z]"); do
  dir=$(dirname "$file")
  base=$(basename "$file")
  newname=$(echo "$base" | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]')
  mv "$file" "$dir/$newname"
done

# Replace spaces with dashes
for file in $(find . -type f -name "* *.md"); do
  newname=$(echo "$file" | sed 's/ /-/g')
  mv "$file" "$newname"
done
` ``

### Special Cases

**Single-Word Files** (No Separator Needed):
` ``text
✅ readme.md
✅ license.md
✅ changelog.md
✅ contributing.md
✅ security.md
` ``

**Acronyms and Abbreviations** (Lowercase):
` ``text
✅ api-reference.md            (not API-Reference.md)
✅ html-guide.md               (not HTML-Guide.md)
✅ ci-pipeline.md              (not CI-Pipeline.md)
✅ sql-queries.md              (not SQL-Queries.md)
` ``

